main event: The report describes an unidentified aerial object observed by a witness on their family farm.
interesting points: The object was described as bright white in color and elongated in shape.
The object did not make any sound and had no visible trail or wings.
The witness estimates the object was moving at a fairly fast speed.
The witness provided compass bearings and elevation angles for when the object first appeared and when it disappeared.
The witness was unsure what the object was and stated 'Don't know -- What is it?'
witnesses: 1 witness, sitting in a station wagon on a family farm
